rows.label: bf05250100_0020
rows.name: What kind of person was Adel?

rows.label: bf05250100_0040
rows.name: No, no, it's fine. I was just wondering.

rows.label: bf05250100_0070
rows.name: I was only there for a very brief time before I went to sleep, but...

rows.label: bf05250100_0080
rows.name:
In Hikari-chan's memories, 
he was more pure and courageous than anyone.

rows.label: bf05250100_0090
rows.name: A strong and wonderful adult man...

rows.label: bf05250100_0112
rows.name: ...And you remind her of him a lot.

rows.label: bf05250100_0120
rows.name: I see, so I resemble him...

rows.label: bf05250100_0130
rows.name:
Hehehe, I'll probably get scolded 
for saying unnecessary things again.

rows.label: bf05250100_0150
rows.name: I agree with her, you know.
